OL,3,CMiners' strike at 40: The story of a
OL,4,Cpit community through one camera lens
OL,6,FPhotographer Kieth Pattison told Jonny
OL,7,FBlair how he came to document the
OL,8,Fminers' strike in Easington
OL,10,FIn 1984, Keith Pattison was a
OL,11,Fphotographer specialising in
OL,12,Fdocumenting arts projects in Newcastle.
OL,14,FDuring March of that year, the near
OL,15,F23,000 men of the County Durham and
OL,16,FNorthumberland coalfields walked out
OL,17,Fin what became one of the biggest
OL,18,Findustrial actions in British history.
