OL,3,CMiners' strike at 40: The story of a
OL,4,Cpit community through one camera lens
OL,6,FThe miners' strike hit headlines and
OL,7,Fhit the communities dependent on the
OL,8,Fpits even harder.
OL,10,FKeith was called upon to record life
OL,11,Fon the ground, and put forward a
OL,12,Fdifferent narrative.
OL,14,F"Someone who commissioned the arts
OL,15,Fprojects had connections with the
OL,16,Funion in Easington," he told ITV Tyne
OL,17,FTees.
OL,19,F"The people in communities didn't feel
OL,20,Fas though their voices were being
OL,21,Fheard.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/9
