OL,3,CMiners' strike at 40: The story of a
OL,4,Cpit community through one camera lens
OL,6,FWhile Keith captured the every day
OL,7,Freality of the miners' strike for
OL,8,Fthose in Easington, he was also there
OL,9,Ffor its toughest days.
OL,11,F"A month in there was this huge push
OL,12,Fand a huge presence from the police,
OL,13,Ffor a week, to actually get a striking
OL,14,Fminer into the pit," he explained.
OL,16,F"And that built from the Monday right
OL,17,Fthrough to the Friday when the place
OL,18,Fwas absolutely flooded with police.
