OL,3,CMiners' strike at 40: The story of a
OL,4,Cpit community through one camera lens
OL,6,F"And looking through the camera you
OL,7,Fwere in the middle of things that
OL,8,Fyou'd only seen in history books, and
OL,9,FI was thinking I'd never seen this
OL,10,Fbefore.
OL,12,F"It was a bit overwhelming but the
OL,13,Fgreat thing was, on the Friday, it was
OL,14,Falmost like photographs were just
OL,15,Fthrowing themselves down my lens."
