OL,3,CMiners' strike at 40: The story of a
OL,4,Cpit community through one camera lens
OL,6,FIt was on Ascot Street in the village
OL,7,Fthat Keith snapped an image which
OL,8,Frepresented what he was trying to
OL,9,Fachieve with his work.JHe said: "It
OL,10,Fwas actually trying to find the simple
OL,11,Fimages that described a more complex
OL,12,Foperation.
OL,14,F"From Ascot Street I was perhaps about
OL,15,Ffifty yards away and spotted a woman
OL,16,Fcome to a window with a newborn baby
OL,17,Fin her arms.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/9
